title: 2014–15 TFF Third League
text: The 2014–15 <a href="TFF%20Third%20League">TFF Third League</a> (also known as "<a href="Spor-Toto">Spor-Toto</a> Third League" due to sponsorship reasons) is the 14th season of the league since its establishment in 2001 as the fourth level division; and the 44th season of the third league in <a href="Turkey">Turkish</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> since its establishment in 1967–68 (before 2001 league was played as third level division).
